OL,7,FSix ads for an Islamic investment
OL,8,Fplatform showing US dollar and euro
OL,9,Fbanknotes on fire have been banned
OL,10,Fafter a regulator ruled they were
OL,11,Flikely to cause serious offence.
OL,13,FThe posters for Wahed Invest, seen in
OL,14,FSeptember and October on Transport for
OL,15,FLondon (TfL) services including tubes
OL,16,Fand buses, featured images of Muslim
OL,17,Fpreacher Ismail ibn Musa Menk and
OL,18,FRussian former professional mixed
OL,19,Fmartial artist Khabib Abdulmanapovich
OL,20,Fsurrounded by the flaming banknotes.
