OL,4,Cshowing burning US and euro banknotes
OL,5,Cbanned
OL,7,FThey showed the two men pointing
OL,8,Fupwards with their index fingers and
OL,9,Flarge text stating "Join the Money
OL,10,FRevolution" above Wahed's logo.
OL,12,FThree of the posters showed Mr Menk
OL,13,Fholding an open briefcase filled with
OL,14,FUS dollar and euro banknotes on fire,
OL,15,Fwith two of them stating "Withdraw
OL,16,Ffrom Exploitation" and "Withdraw from
OL,17,FRiba".
