OL,7,FA poster stated: "Charging people to
OL,8,Fborrow money was once called
OL,9,Fexploitation. Sadly, that perception
OL,10,Fhas changed and now interest has
OL,11,Fcaused a massive wealth gap, enriching
OL,12,Fthe few while the majority get poorer.
OL,13,FJoin the growing community moving
OL,14,Ftheir money to a fairer system, one
OL,15,Fthat serves you! Download Wahed now.
OL,16,FJoin the Money Revolution."
OL,18,FThe Advertising Standards Authority
OL,19,F(ASA) received 75 complaints that the
OL,20,Fads were offensive.
