OL,7,FTfL told the ASA that it believed the
OL,8,Fads complied with its ad policy and
OL,9,Fthe regulator's code.
OL,11,FIt said it had received some
OL,12,Fcomplaints about the ads and had
OL,13,Fpaused all campaigns from Wahed Invest
OL,14,Fpending the outcome of an
OL,15,Finvestigation.
