OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F407A1736359938
OL,3,CAds for Islamic investment platform
OL,4,Cshowing burning US and euro banknotes
OL,5,Cbanned
OL,7,FThe ASA said all the ads showed the
OL,8,Fwords "The United States of America"
OL,9,Fin flames, and would have been seen by
OL,10,Fmany people, including tourists from
OL,11,Fthe United States and eurozone
OL,12,Fcountries.
OL,14,FThe ASA said: "We acknowledged Wahed
OL,15,FInvest's view that the burning of
OL,16,Fbanknotes illustrated that money which
OL,17,Fgrew at a rate lower than inflation
OL,18,Fdecreased in value in real terms.
OL,26,@pD@GOUpD@dO]vD@OOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/11
