CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F407A1736359938
OL,3,CAds for Islamic investment platform
OL,4,Cshowing burning US and euro banknotes
OL,5,Cbanned
OL,7,F"The ads represented the expression
OL,8,Fthat viewers' money was 'going up in
OL,9,Fflames' and that images of burning
OL,10,Fmoney were commonly encountered.
OL,12,F"However, regardless of whether
OL,13,Fviewers would have understood that
OL,14,Fmessage or understood it as a defiant
OL,15,Fact designed to show a challenge to
OL,16,Ffinancial institutions, the currencies
OL,17,Fwhich were burned in all of the ads
OL,18,Fwere clearly visible as US dollar and
OL,19,Feuro banknotes.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/11
