CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F407A1736359938
OL,3,CAds for Islamic investment platform
OL,4,Cshowing burning US and euro banknotes
OL,5,Cbanned
OL,7,F"We considered some viewers,
OL,8,Fparticularly people from the United
OL,9,FStates or eurozone countries, would
OL,10,Fhave viewed their nation's currency as
OL,11,Fbeing culturally significant and a
OL,12,Fsymbol of their national identity.
OL,14,F"Although we acknowledged Wahed
OL,15,FInvest's view that they had not
OL,16,Fdirectly criticised a specific group,
OL,17,Fand that depictions of burning
OL,18,Fbanknotes were commonly encountered,
OL,19,Fwe considered the burning of banknotes
OL,20,Fwould have caused serious offence to
OL,21,Fsome viewers.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/11
