OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F407A1736359938
OL,3,CAds for Islamic investment platform
OL,4,Cshowing burning US and euro banknotes
OL,5,Cbanned
OL,7,F"We therefore concluded that the ads
OL,8,Fwere likely to cause serious offence."
OL,10,FA TfL spokeswoman said: "All adverts
OL,11,Fare reviewed against TfL's policy, as
OL,12,Fwell as the Committees of Advertising
OL,13,FPractice (CAP) Code before being
OL,14,Fapproved to run on the network. It is
OL,15,Fabsolutely right that any further
OL,16,Fconcerns about adverts following this
OL,17,Fprocess are referred to the ASA as the
OL,18,Findependent advertising regulator.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@fO]rD@YOU
