OL,3,CAds for Islamic investment platform
OL,4,Cshowing burning US and euro banknotes
OL,5,Cbanned
OL,7,F"We supported the ASA's investigation
OL,8,Finto the advertising campaign from
OL,9,FWahed and, following the outcome, we
OL,10,Fwill apply the findings when
OL,11,Fconsidering any future campaigns."
OL,13,FWahed launched in the US in 2019 and
OL,14,Fis backed by the oil giant Saudi
OL,15,FAramco.
OL,17,FWahed has been approached for comment.
